We recommend that Management:

a) Require the concerned officials to submit the original copy of the CAs on travel made with GSIS, Butuan City;

b) Direct the staff of the late former Mayor to submit the approved TOs for the travel made outside the province. 

c) Direct the concerned officials/employees to submit justification for travels without specific purpose and those which deviates from the original TO, for evaluation in audit. Failure to provide the same shall render the transaction irregular, thereby disallowable in audit; 

d) Direct all employees to be responsible and prudent in processing their individual claims to ensure that complete and only valid supporting documents were attached thereto, otherwise these shall not be passed in pre-audit of the Accounting Section; and

e) Instruct the Municipal Accountant to properly scrutinize the completeness and propriety of the supporting documents to prevent suspension or disallowance of transactions.

